content:
The Analytics for Corporate and Investment Banking app is designed to help understand Corporate and Investment Banking deals. It includes details about deal participants, products, and parties.

To create and manage the app: FSC Analytics Admin, CRM Analytics Plus Admin permissions are needed. To use the app: FSC Analytics User, CRM Analytics Plus User permissions are required.

The template creates datasets, recipes, and dashboards to help understand Corporate and Investment Banking deals.

Salesforce Org Requirements:

* Make sure you have the FSC Apps license.
* Your org must have at least one of each record type: FinancialDeal, and Account.
* Set Salesforce Org permissions.
* Schedule a recipe to sync data.
* Embed the Analytics for Corporate and Investment Banking app in Lightning Experience pages and Salesforce Classic experiences.

Datasets:

* Financial Deal
* Financial Deal Snapshot
* Financial Deal Participant
* Financial Deal Party
* Financial Deal Product
* Interaction
* Interaction Attendee
* Interaction Participant
* Interaction Summary
* Interaction Summary Participant
title: Deploying Corporate and Investment Banking Analytics
